snippet.title: Puyo Puyo Sun All Openings HD (Arcade/PC/N64, PS1/Saturn, and GBC)
snippet.description:
Arcade/PC/N64 intro: 0:00
Playstation/Sega Saturn intro: 0:46
Game Boy Colour intro: 2:52

Shoutout to Puyonexus for the English patch of the game: http://puyonexus.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=898

It's possible to play Puyo Puyo games with online multiplayer for free. Click this video to find out more: http://youtu.be/ZVkVvwZaYp4

Associated Discord server: https://discord.gg/qjTHFRh

Shout out to Puyonexus and King Arthur Pendragon for footage

ぷよぷよSUN, Puyopuyo San
